strings: <voice_0x01000D7A><se_low>*: Before he leaves, Dan offers him a horse.
<voice_0x01000D7B><se_low>*: He must know you posted something there. you've got to judge
<voice_0x01000D7C><se_low>King of tricks: hello media! What a cruel ordeal! Disappointed, I will not leave you again!
<voice_0x01000D7D><se_low>King of tricks: I won't go to this bar again! promise
<voice_0x01000D7F><se_low>King of tricks: <most_heroic> Contact anytime. Where is your next destination?
<voice_0x01000D80><se_low>January: Why not give it another try? Perhaps the old man can enlighten us this time.
<voice_0x01000D82><se_low>January: I'd like to know where the Dumages are. Otherwise we curl up like chickens and stop eating.
<voice_0x01000D83><se_low>King of tricks: Well... it would be simpler if we didn't live in Peckham anymore. But I don't seem to have a choice.
